OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMisty start with some drizzly
OL,6,Frain, and some fog patches for
OL,7,FShetland at first. Remaining cloudy
OL,8,Fwith occasional light rain and some
OL,9,Ffog patches returning to Shetland
OL,10,Flater, but a lot of dry weather too.
OL,11,FPerhaps some late Orkney sunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShetland will remain cloudy
OL,14,Fwith the chance of some mist and
OL,15,Fdrizzle at times. Orkney will be dry
OL,16,Fwith variable cloud and a few clear
OL,17,Fspells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
