OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAnother mostly cloudy day.
OL,6,FShetland may see a little patchy rain
OL,7,Fat times, with the best chance of
OL,8,Fbrighter and warmer conditions over
OL,9,FOrkney.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FIt will
OL,12,Fbe a dry few days with plenty of
OL,13,Fsunshine, and winds will be light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
